Program: The Reith Lectures
Title: War and the State
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00gw9y1
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 22 Apr 1998
This year's Reith lecturer is British military historian and journalist John Keegan. In his third Reith lecture, recorded at King's College London, John Keegan explores the evolving relationship between war and the nation state, the changing nature of sovereignty, and examines whether states need to cause conflict. Show less